The paper discusses the characteristics of Internet AS topologies, which are related to computer networks and network infrastructure. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves data analysis and modeling, which could fall under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
